Class GenInfoRepoStub

  • java.lang.Object
    • clientSide.GenInfoRepoStub
  • public class GenInfoRepoStub
extends java.lang.Object
    This class defines the stub of the GenInfoRepo in the AIRPORT RAPSODY that implements the client-server model (type 2) with static launch of the threads
